text.section:
The Department of Kentucky State Police shall make an annual report to the Legislative Research Commission, not later than December 31 of each year, detailing each notice received pursuant to this section detailing:
The name of the firearms instructor trainer or certified firearms instructor if that instructor trainer or instructor has been arrested or indicted as a result of the notification, otherwise the name shall be omitted;
The precise allegation;
Whether the allegation resulted in arrest or indictment;
Whether the allegation resulted in a trial, and the results of that trial; and
If the defendant was found guilty, the punishment imposed.
